This content management system is being built for my Web Programming class.

Install

- Edit app/config/database.php to match your database configuration. MySQL is the only driver supported.
- Edit app/bootstrap.php
    - Change base_url if needed
- If the base_url is changed in bootstrap.php, RewriteBase in .htaccess must be changed as well.
- Import the cms.sql into your database.
    - Default username: admin
    - Default password: password
    - Be sure to go to the administration section to change your password.